ip (Golshi) 是他活跃的频道“Pakatube!”的记录。 </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="2ek6JUbYHP"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/robocosan-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-hololive-2nd-oldest-vtuber-reaches-the-big-mark/">Roboko-san 订阅人数突破 100 万，成为 Hololive 上第二位达到这一里程碑的资深 VTuber</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Roboko-san 的订阅人数达到 100 万，是 Hololive 上第二位达到这一里程碑的资深 VTuber” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/robocosan-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-hololive-2nd-oldest-vtuber-reaches-the-big-mark/embed/#?secret=vHVivH2Hmm#?secret=2ek6JUbYHP" data-secret="2ek6JUbYHP" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p> *不包括2021年7月1日毕业的Coco Kiryu和2022年2月24日终止合同的Rushia Junha。</p></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0TXe_LYZ4scaW2XMyi5_kw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">AZKi 频道</a>/ <a href="https://twitter.com/AZKi_VDiVA" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">AZKi <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2692.png" alt="⚒" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a> / <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/azki/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">阿兹基</a></p><cite>YouTube / Twitter / Hololive 制作</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="uFMysV53VB"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/azki-to-hold-stream-1-million-yout