</style><p>在韩国的VTuber行业中，利用韩国K-POP文化知识的异世界偶像（ISEGYE IDOL）、StelLive和PLAVE等机构、团体和艺人的知名度正在迅速扩大。 Brave 组合最近的职位空缺可能是为了启动一个利用此类 K-POP 专业知识的新项目（组合和新人才的首次亮相）。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__4" class="wp-block-heading">近期韩国VTuber行业资讯</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="bKH86XWT0d"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vu-entertainment-announced-termination-of-2nd-gen-vtuber-amano-serafi/">V&amp;U Entertainment宣布解除第二代VTuber Amano Serafi合约</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“V&amp;U Entertainment宣布取消第二代VTuber Amano Serafi的合同” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vu-entertainment-announced-termination-of-2nd-gen-vtuber-amano-serafi/embed/#?secret=QqmALuc8hD#?secret=bKH86XWT0d" data-secret="bKH86XWT0d" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="PzPKS9bYRR"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/isegye-idol-ranked-world-no-2-in-average-youtube-subscribers/">《异世界偶像》6位VTuber平均订阅人数跃升至全球第二位</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“就 6 位 VTuber 的平均订阅人数而言，《异世界偶像》已上升至全球第二位” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/isegye-idol-ranked-world-no-2-in-average-youtube-subscribers/embed/#?secret=3nI2MeAYmO#?secret=PzPKS9bYRR" data-secret="PzPKS9bYRR" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="NNhTTU7Ge1"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/korean-authorities-fine-twitch-plann